genresAdvancedInfo.name: deep funk ostentacao
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Deep funk ostentacao is a Brazilian subgenre of funk music that originated in the favelas of São Paulo. It features heavy basslines, aggressive rapping, and flashy, ostentatious lyrics about money, cars, and luxury. The sound is characterized by its mix of funk, hip-hop, and electronic music, and has become increasingly popular in Brazil in recent years.
